                    <img src="~/Content/images/get-now-img2.png" />
                </div>
                <figcaption class="col-md-6">
                    <h2 class="title-h2"> Receiving the loan money</h2>
                    <div class="get-text">Once the lender approves your loan and you accept the loan terms, your loan will be deposited directly in your bank account, usually as soon as the next day.</div>
